<h2>Administrare cont</h2>
<div class='clearfix'></div>
<form class="form-horizontal" role="form" action="" method='post'>
<div class='row well well-lg login_form'>
	<div class="help-block text-left">Va rugam sa completati cu atentie campurile de mai jos.</div>
	<div class='col-sm-7 col-xs-12 text-left'>
		<div class="form-group form-group-lg">
			<div class="input-group col-sm-7">
				<div class="input-group-addon" id='username'><span class='glyphicon glyphicon-user'></span></div>
				<input type="text" name='username' class="form-control" placeholder="Utilizator/Username ..." value="" aria-describedby="username">
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="form-group form-group-lg">
			<div class="input-group col-sm-7">
				<div class="input-group-addon" id='parola'><span class='glyphicon glyphicon-lock'></span></div>
				<input type="password" name="password" class="form-control" placeholder="Parola dvs ..." value="" aria-describedby="parola">
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="form-group form-group-lg">
			<div class="input-group col-sm-7">
				<button type="submit" name="login" class="btn btn-info btn-lg">Autentificare</button>
			</div>
		</div>
		<p><a href="{USER_FORGOT_LINK}">Recuperare parola</a></p>
		<p><a href="{CONT_NOU}">Cont nou</a></p>
	</div>
	<div class='col-sm-5 col-xs-12 text-center'>
		<p class="article_details_title"> Ai nevoie de ajutor?</p>
		<p class="help_phone">Ne puteti contacta de Luni-Vineri la numarul de telefon: <br><b>0727-380-368</b>.</p>
	</div>
</div>
</form>